#   - Server will automatically use JSON file storage
#   - No PostgreSQL installation required

# For LOCAL DEVELOPMENT with PostgreSQL:
#   - Install PostgreSQL: https://www.postgresql.org/download/
#   - Create database: createdb cinestream_db
#   - Uncomment and update the line below:
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://username:password@localhost:5432/cinestream_db

# For PRODUCTION (Render, Railway, etc.):
#   - Render will automatically set DATABASE_URL from your PostgreSQL service
#   - Railway will automatically set DATABASE_URL from your PostgreSQL plugin
#   - Just deploy and it will work!

